In a video mocking Trump, Fox says: “Donald, you suck so much at this job…” and even refers to him as "a rotting Halloween pumpkin." JOHANNESBURG - Former Mexican president Vicente Fox has hilariously announced his plan to run for the US Presidency. In a video mocking Donald Trump, Fox says: “Donald, you suck so much at this job…” and even refers to him as "a rotting Halloween pumpkin." Fox is not new to the Trump-bashing game, he’s in the past posted tweets and videos belittling and making fun of the US President. **WARNING: This video contains strong language. ** 